OL,3,CMum of riot boy, 12, to appear in
OL,4,Ccourt after 'missing son's hearing for
OL,5,CIbiza'
OL,7,FThe mother of one of Britain's
OL,8,Fyoungest criminals involved in last
OL,9,Fmonth's riots has been summoned by a
OL,10,Fjudge, after missing her son's court
OL,11,Fappearance to go to Ibiza.
OL,13,FThe 12 year old, who cannot be
OL,14,Fidentified for legal reasons, admitted
OL,15,Ftwo counts of violent disorder at
OL,16,FManchester Crown Court.
