OL,3,CMum of riot boy, 12, to appear in
OL,4,Ccourt after 'missing son's hearing for
OL,5,CIbiza'
OL,7,FOn Monday 2 September District Judge
OL,8,FJoanne Hirst told Manchester
OL,9,FMagistrates' Court she was "frankly
OL,10,Fastonished" that the boy's mum had
OL,11,Fdecided to fly abroad for a five-day
OL,12,Fsunshine break, with her son due in
OL,13,Fcourt for his part in violent disorder.
OL,15,FDistrict Judge Hirst adjourned
OL,16,Fsentencing the boy and ordered a
OL,17,Fparental summons so the mother must
OL,18,Fappear before the court to explain her
OL,19,Fabsence.
