OL,3,CMum of riot boy, 12, to appear in
OL,4,Ccourt after 'missing son's hearing for
OL,5,CIbiza'
OL,7,FThe judge had been told the boy's
OL,8,Fmother was not present because she had
OL,9,Fbooked a holiday in July and gone
OL,10,Fabroad on Sunday 1 September.
OL,12,FShe was only due to fly back to the UK
OL,13,Fon Thursday, missing his sentencing
OL,14,Fhearing last Monday, the court heard.
OL,16,FThe youngster, who was accompanied to
OL,17,Fcourt by his uncle, had earlier
OL,18,Fadmitted being part of a mob that
OL,19,Fattacked a bus outside a hotel housing
OL,20,Fasylum seekers in Manchester on 31
OL,21,FJuly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
