OL,5,CIbiza'
OL,7,FDays later on 3 August, in Manchester
OL,8,Fcity centre, he was part of a group
OL,9,Ffilmed kicking the windows of a vape
OL,10,Fshop and throwing a missile at a
OL,11,Fpolice van.
OL,13,FDozens of towns and cities saw
OL,14,Fviolence erupt following the killing
OL,15,Fof three young girls at a Taylor Swift-
OL,16,Fthemed dance class in Southport on 29
OL,17,FJuly.
