OL,3,CMum of riot boy, 12, to appear in
OL,4,Ccourt after 'missing son's hearing for
OL,5,CIbiza'
OL,7,FDistrict Judge Hirst thanked the boy's
OL,8,Funcle for accompanying his nephew to
OL,9,Fcourt in his mother's absence, but
OL,10,Fadded: "One day before the hearing we
OL,11,Ffind out the mum has gone on holiday
OL,12,Fand is not with her son, who played a
OL,13,Fgreater part in the recent civil
OL,14,Fdisorder than any adult or child I've
OL,15,Fseen coming through these courts.
OL,17,F"I'm frankly astonished.
